#: translate_tmp:45
msgid "Upload screenshots into your Dropbox"
msgstr "Lanlwythwch sgrinluniau i'ch Dropbox"

#: translate_tmp:123
msgid "There was an error receiving the authentication URL."
msgstr "Roedd gwall wrth dderbyn yr URL dilysu"

#: translate_tmp:128
msgid ""
"Please click on the button below to authorize with Dropbox. Press 'Apply' "
"when you are done."
msgstr ""
"Pwyswch y botwm isod i awdurdodi gyda Dropdox. Pwyswch 'Gosod' ar ôl gorffen."

#: translate_tmp:129
msgid "Authorize with Dropbox"
msgstr "Awdurdodi gyda Dropbox"

#: translate_tmp:132
msgid "Authorize"
msgstr "Awdurdodi"

#: translate_tmp:142
msgid "There was an error authenticating with Dropbox."
msgstr "Roedd gwall wrth ddilysu gyda Dropbox"

#: translate_tmp:212
msgid ""
"Maybe you or Dropbox revoked or expired an access token. Please close this "
"dialog and try again. Your account will be re-authenticated the next time "
"you upload a file."
msgstr ""
"Efallai gwnaethoch chi neu Dropbox dynnu tocyn mynediad. Ceuwch y deialog "
"hwn a cheisio eto. Caiff eich cyfrif ei ail-ddilysu y tro nesaf rydych chi'n "
"lanlwytho ffeil."

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid "Upload screenshots to imagebanana.com"
msgstr "Lanlwythwch sgrinluniau i imagebanana.com"

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid "ImageShack is providing free image hosting"
msgstr "Mae ImageShack yn gwesteio'r delweddau yn rhad ac am ddim"

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid ""
"Imgur is used to share photos with social networks and online communities, "
"and has the funniest pictures from all over the Internet"
msgstr ""
"Caiff Imgur ei ddefnyddio i rannu lluniau gyda rhwydweithiau cymdeithasol a "
"chymunedau ar-lein ac mae ganddo'r delweddau mwyaf doniol o'r we gyfan"

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid ""
"imm.io is a one-click easy image sharer, perfect if you want to upload an "
"image to show your friends or link from other sites"
msgstr ""
"Mae immo.io yn ddatrysiad un-clic er mwyn rhannu delweddau yn hawdd, sy'n "
"berffaith os ydych chi am lanlwytho delwedd i dangos i'ch ffrindiau neu i "
"gysylltu o safleoedd eraill"

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid "Upload screenshots to itmages.com"
msgstr "Lanlwythwch sgrinluniau i itmages.com"

#: translate_tmp:45
msgid "Minus is the simplest free file sharing platform online"
msgstr ""
"Minus yw'r platfform rhannu ffeiliau ar-lein rhad ac am ddim symlaf sydd ar "
"gael"

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid "Upload screenshots to ompldr.org"
msgstr "Lanlwythwch sgrinluniau i ompldr.org"

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid "Upload screenshots to pix.toile-libre.org"
msgstr "Lanlwythwch sgrinluniau i pix.toile-libre.org"

#: translate_tmp:45
msgid "TwitPic lets you share media on Twitter in real-time"
msgstr "Mae TwitPic yn eich caniatàu chi i rannu cyfrwng ar Twitter yn syth"

#: translate_tmp:44
msgid "Upload screenshots to ubuntu-pics.de"
msgstr "Lanlwythwch sgrinluniau i ubuntu-pics.de"
